title: Russia can offer India & Brazil spot in expanded UNSC, but thereâ€™s a catch
description: In his address at the plenary session of the UN World Peace Forum in Beijing, Russian Ambassador to China, Andrey Denisov, said that Moscow supports expanding the UN Security Council (UNSC), but not by admitting Germany and Japan. As per RT report, he added that Russia is open to the idea of membership for India and Brazil, but not Germany and Japan, "since this will not change the internal balance in any way." He claimed that the Security Council has become a place where "the Western colleagues carry out propaganda, presenting their views as the ultimate truth." Watch this video for more information.|#russia #india #unsc #brazil #germany #japan #unitednations #west #ukraine #russiaukrainewar #narendramodi #vladimirputin

title: Geramnya Kapolda Metro Jaya: Parkir Liar di Senopati, Macet Kok Dibiarkan!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Kapolda Metro Jaya Irjen Fadil Imran geram karena adanya kemacetan di Jakarta yang bersumber dari parkir liar seperti di kawasan Jalan Suryo dan Senopati.||||Kapolda Metro Jaya minta petugas langsung derek yang parkir sembarangan serta menaruh petugas di wilayah tersebut.||||"Kalau perlu ada posko lalu lintas bersama DLLAJR di situ. Saya akan lihat mulai hari ini ke depan. Saya mau Anda taruh derek di situ, Anda taruh anggota di situ, begitu ada yang parkir sembarangan, tarik," seru Fadil.||||Baca Juga Adu Tinju Lawan Kapolda Metro Jaya, Cuma Emak-Emak Ini yang Berani! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305617/adu-tinju-lawan-kapolda-metro-jaya-cuma-emak-emak-ini-yang-berani||||"Macet kok dibiarkan. Nah di tempat lain juga di Jaksel, Jakut, Jaktim khususnya di tempat-tempat yang sangat mengganggu kepentingan umum," tambahnya.||||"Saya minta teman-teman di lalu lintas sudah mulai berbicara bagaimana mengurai kemacetan. Kalau macet karena volume bukan macet ya terjadi peningkatan, nggak apa-apa. Tapi kalau macet karena memang parkir sembarangan, padahal sudah ada pedestrian itu yang menurut saya harus kita tertibkan," pungkas Fadil.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306350/geramnya-kapolda-metro-jaya-parkir-liar-di-senopati-macet-kok-dibiarkan

title: UK ministers Rishi Sunak and Sajid Javid resign from government - BBC News
description: The UK chancellor and health secretary have resigned from government, saying they no longer have confidence in Prime Minister Boris Johnson.|Rishi Sunak said the public expected government to be conducted "properly, competently and seriously", while Sajid Javid said government was not "acting in the national interest".|Meanwhile, Education Secretary Nadhim Zahawi has been picked as chancellor and Steve Barclay, Johnson's chief of staff, now becomes health secretary.|The two resignations came minutes after the PM apologised for appointing MP Chris Pincher to a government role after being told about a misconduct complaint against the MP.|Mr Pincher has denied allegations of sexual misconduct.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

description: SURABAYA, KOMPAS.TV  Tim Gabungan Polda Jawa Timur dan Polres Jombang melakukan penyergapan tersangka DPO berinisial MSA atas kasus pencabulan lima korban santri putri di Jombang.||||Namun, MSA yang diduga berada di dalam iring-iringan berhasil kabur pada Minggu, 3 Juli 2022.||||Kabid Humas Polda Jawa Timur menjelaskan kronologi penyergapan DPO kasus pencabulan santri Jombang yang kabur ini.||||Ada tiga mobil iring-iringan yang menghalangi proses penangkapan tersangka MSA, salah satu mobil menabrak salah satu anggota hingga jatuh.||||Baca Juga Anak Kiai di Jombang Jadi Tersangka Pencabulan Santri, Ayah Tersangka: Itu Hanya Fitnah! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306333/anak-kiai-di-jombang-jadi-tersangka-pencabulan-santri-ayah-tersangka-itu-hanya-fitnah||||Proses kejar-kejaran terjadi hingga anggota mengamankan 1 unit kendaraan dengan dua orang penumpang dan satu supir yang melarikan diri.||||Sejauh ini polisi telah mengamankan 5 orang saksi untuk diperiksa.||||Sebelumnya pada tahun 2019, MSA melakukan tindak pidana pencabulan kepada 5 orang santriwati dan telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka pada tahun 2020 oleh PN Jombang hingga kini tersangka MSA masih dinyatakan buron.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306358/kronologi-lengkap-penyergapan-dpo-kasus-pencabulan-santri-jombang

title: â€˜Kaaliâ€™ row: Mahua Moitra unfollows TMC on Twitter, after party denounces â€˜meat-eaterâ€™ remark
description: A day after the Trinamool Congress distanced itself from Mahua Moitra's comments on Goddess Kali, the party MP has unfollowed TMC's official Twitter handle. Moitra is now only following TMC supremo and West Bengal Chief Minister Mamata Banerjee on Twitter. Mahua Moitra is yet to react to the development. Moitra, while responding to a question at a conclave on the controversy over 'Kaali' film poster showing a woman dressed as Goddess Kali smoking a cigarette, said that her Goddess was meat-eating and alcohol accepting. After widespread criticism on social media, Moitra said later on Tuesday that she â€œdid not back any film or poster or mention the word smokingâ€. Watch this video for more details.|#kaali #mahuamoitra #tmc #twitter #india #hindugod #goddesskali

title: [Full] Penjelasan Lengkap PPATK Setop Sementara 60 Rekening Yayasan ACT!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Kepala PPATK Ivan Yustiavandana mengatakan pihaknya menghentikan sementara transaksi keuangan di 60 rekening atas nama Yayasan Aksi Cepat Tanggap (ACT).||||Rekening tersebut terdapat di 33 penyedia jasa keuangan.||||"Per hari ini, PPATK menghentikan sementara transaksi atas 60 rekening atas nama entitas yayasan tadi di 33 penyedia jasa keuangan sudah kami hentikan," kata Kepala PPATK Ivan Yustiavandana dalam konferensi pers, Rabu (6/7/2022).||||Baca Juga Mahfud MD Minta PPATK Bantu Polri Usut Kasus Dugaan Penyelewengan Donasi ACT di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306375/mahfud-md-minta-ppatk-bantu-polri-usut-kasus-dugaan-penyelewengan-donasi-act||||Sebelumnya, Kemensos juga telah mencabut izin Penyelenggaraan Pengumpulan Uang dan Barang yang diberikan kepada Yayasan Aksi Cepat Tanggap (ACT).||||Mensos Ad Interim Muhadjir Effendy mengatakan alasan mencabut izin PUB milik ACT karena ada indikasi terkait pelanggaran terhadap peraturan Mensos.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306409/full-penjelasan-lengkap-ppatk-setop-sementara-60-rekening-yayasan-act

title: â€˜Beheadâ€™ Nupur Sharma video: Ajmer Dargah cleric Salman Chisti nabbed by Rajasthan police
description: Salman Chishti, the cleric of Ajmer Sharif Dargah, who made provocative comments against suspended BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma in response to her remarks on the Prophet, has been arrested by the Rajasthan Police on Tuesday night. Cops say that Chishti is a history-sheeter and had released a video announcing reward for anyone who beheads Nupur Sharma in an inebriated state. Vikas Sangwan, Additional Superintendent of Police (ASP) of Ajmer district said that the video was extensively circulated through WhatsApp and that he too had received the clip. He said that police took swift action and launched a massive manhunt to nab Chishti. Watch this video for more information.|#nupursharma #prophetinsult #ajmerdargah #cleric #bjp #rajasthan #ajmer #india #prophetmuhammad

title: Bawa Foto Eril, Ridwan Kamil dan Keluarga Berdoa Depan Kabah Dipimpin Gus Miftah
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil bersama keluarga lantunkan doa untuk Eril di depan Kabah, Masjidil Haram.||||Hal tersebut diabadikan dan diunggah di instagram penceramah Gus Miftah. Nampak Ridwan Kamil di sana bersama sang istri Atalia, dan Zara.||||Gus Miftah pimpin tahlil untuk Eril di depan kabah. Sebelumnya juga nampak Gus Miftah ajak Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga bertawaf di lokasi tersebut.||||Baca Juga Momen Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Tawaf di Masjidil Haram, Diabadikan Penceramah Gus Miftah di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306068/momen-ridwan-kamil-dan-atalia-tawaf-di-masjidil-haram-diabadikan-penceramah-gus-miftah||||Ridwan Kamil berangkat haji karena ditugaskan memimpin belasan ribu jemaah calon haji asal Jawa Barat.||||Ia berangkat sebagai Amirul Hajj, yang bertiugas memastikan kelancaran dan kemanan peserta atau jemaah haji asal Jabar.||||Dalam sebuah kesempatan, Ridwan Kamil meminta maaf karena tahun ini hanya 45 persen dari total kuota jemaah haji Jawa Barat yang bisa berangkat.||||Ia meminta calon jemaah yang belum bisa berangkat tahun ini agar bersabar menunggu kesempatan berikutnya.||||Ridwan Kamil juga meniatkan berhaji atas nama sang anak, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||RK mengaku telah berpamitan sekaligus berziarah ke makam Eril di Cimaung, Kab. Bandung.||||"Sekalian di momen ini, saya akan berhaji atas nama almarhum Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz. Karenanya, tadi pagi ziarah, pamit dan berdoa di makam Eril."||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306412/bawa-foto-eril-ridwan-kamil-dan-keluarga-berdoa-depan-kabah-dipimpin-gus-miftah

title: History in IAF: Fighter pilot father-daughter duo first to fly in same formation, win praise
description: Fighter pilots, Air Commodore Sanjay Sharma and Flying Officer Ananya of the Indian Air Force (IAF) have created history by becoming the first father-daughter pair to fly in a formation of jets. The two officers flew in a formation of British-origin Hawk-132 advanced jet trainers (AJTs) at the Bidar airbase in Karnataka on May 30, but the unprecedented moment went unnoticed for weeks, until their photographs surfaced on Tuesday. The development came seven years after IAF decided to induct women into the fighter stream, a turning point for them in combat. Watch this video for more information.|#fighterpilots #fatherdaughter #indianairforce #india #sanjaysharma #ananyasharma #iaf #bidar #karnataka

title: Kemensos Cabut Izin ACT Terkait Dugaan Penyelewengan Dana Sosial
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Kementerian Sosial (Kemensos) mencabut izin yang telah diberikan kepada Yayasan Aksi Cepat Tanggap (ACT) pada tahun 2022 terkait Penyelenggaraan Pengumpulan Uang dan Barang atau PUB.||||Menteri Sosial Ad Interim Muhadjir Effendi mengungkapkan, bahwa pencabutan itu dinyatakan dalam Keputusan Menteri Sosial Republik Indonesia Nomor 133/HUK/2022 tanggal 5 Juli 2022.||||Pencabutan ini dilakukan karena adanya dugaan pelanggaran peraturan yang dilakukan Yayasan.||||"Jadi alasan kita mencabut dengan pertimbangan karena adanya indikasi pelanggaran terhadap Peraturan Menteri Sosial sampai nanti menunggu hasil pemeriksaan dari Inspektorat Jenderal baru akan ada ketentuan sanksi lebih lanjut", kata Muhadjir sebagaimana dikutip dari Kompas.com, (6/7).||||Baca Juga Kemensos: ACT Bukan Dicabut Izin Organisasinya, Tapi Izin Pengumpulan Uang dan Barang di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306285/kemensos-act-bukan-dicabut-izin-organisasinya-tapi-izin-pengumpulan-uang-dan-barang||||Diberitakan sebelumnya, muncul dugaan penyelewengan dana donasi oleh petinggi ACT.||||Selain itu, dalam laporan tersebut diketahui bahwa petinggi ACT disebut menerima sejumlah fasilitas mewah.||||Presiden Lembaga ACT, Ibnu Hajar membenarkan gaji petinggi ACT khususnya jabatan presiden mencapai Rp 250 juta per bulan.||||Gaji fantastis itu mulai diterapkan pada awal tahun 2021.||||Lembaga juga mengakui ada pemotongan sebesar 13,7 persen dari total uang donasi yang diperoleh per tahun.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306298/kemensos-cabut-izin-act-terkait-dugaan-penyelewengan-dana-sosial

title: Future Agniveers opt for Agnipath; IAF gets 7.5 lakh applications, 10000 women apply for navy
description: The defence forces recruitment scheme 'Agnipath', which had drawn nation-wide protests, has attracted more applications in the Indian Air Force (IAF) this year than it did in the last recruitment drive. The IAF said 7,49,899 future 'Agniveers' have applied under 'Agnipath'. IAF also said that the online application window for the scheme is finally closed, and has received a tremendous response from aspirants. As per reports, Army aspirants are also asking IAF and the defence ministry to extend the application deadline. Meanwhile, 10000 women have applied under 'Agnipath' in the Indian Navy. Up to 20% of candidates that the navy plans to recruit under the government's new scheme for short-term induction of soldiers are expected to be women. Watch this video for more information.|#agnipath #agniveer #indianairforce #indiannavy #agnipathschemeprotest #indianarmy #agnipathscheme #women #defencenews

title: Respons Mendag Zulkifli Hasan Soal Harga Cabai Mahal: Tidak Apa-apalah ya
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Menteri Perdagangan Zulkifli Hasan mengatakan bahwa kenaikan harga cabai bukanlah masalah.||||Dia juga menilai kenaikan ini sebagai bentuk bonus untuk para petani cabai di musim panen.||||"Tapi kalau cabai saya kira ndak apa-apalah ya. Sesekali petani bisa panen biar untung ya." Kata Zulkifli Hasan saat mengunjungi Pasar Ciracas, Jakarta Timur, Selasa (5/7).||||Baca Juga Harga Cabai di Tingkat Petani Rp 75 Ribu Per Kilogram, Di Pasar Melambung di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306103/harga-cabai-di-tingkat-petani-rp-75-ribu-per-kilogram-di-pasar-melambung||||Selain itu, Zulkifli Hasan menyebutkan solusi dari harga cabe yang tinggi yaitu tanaman hidroponik cabai, di mana panen cabai tidak terpengaruhi oleh musim.||||Dia mengatakan bahwa sistem hidroponik ini merupakan salah satu bentuk solusi jangka panjang yang akan dilakukan oleh Menteri Pertanian.||||Sebelumnya, harga cabai tidak stabil.||||Tercatat pada Selasa (5/7) di Pasar Ciracas harga cabai keriting dan cabai rawit berada di atas Rp100 ribu.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306246/respons-mendag-zulkifli-hasan-soal-harga-cabai-mahal-tidak-apa-apalah-ya

title: Man accused of luring 13-year-old Edmonton girl makes court appearance as child returns home
description: The man accused in the child luring case of a 13-year-old Edmonton girl made a brief court appearance on Tuesday in Oregon.|40-year-old Noah Madrano is facing multiple charges in the U.S. and Canada.|Meanwhile, Madrano's family released a statement stating, â€œWe love Noah unconditionally, which includes loving him even through the most unthinkable of acts. Our love does not mean that we condone, excuse, or minimize these acts â€” vehemently, we do not."|The Edmonton teenager was last seen on Friday, June 24, at around 8:30 a.m. in the area of 131 Avenue and 91 Street, which is next to Killarney Junior High School. Edmonton police said she was found in Oregon on the morning of July 2 and a man was arrested for child luring.|Police believe the two met online.|According to the Clackamas County District Attorneyâ€™s office in Oregon City, Madrano was taken into custody through a joint effort by the Oregon City Police Department and the Federal Bureau of Investigation on July 2, 2022 in Oregon City.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8968258/man-accused-child-luring-13-year-old-edmonton-girl-statement/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews

title: Suspect In Highland Park Shooting Faces 7 First-Degree Murder Charges
description: The suspect in the Highland Park, Illinois shooting Robert E. Crimo III has been officially charged with seven counts of first-degree murder. title: My chicken curry udon... Japanese style | Marionâ€™s Kitchen
description: Considered real Japanese comfort food, Japanese-style curry is typically eaten as curry katsu (a curry sauce with rice and sliced, crumbed chicken or pork) but is excellent in a soup iteration for thick, chewy udon noodles. Here, Iâ€™ve given it a boost with chicken mince (you could use turkey or pork mince instead) and finished with a whole raft of fun toppings. If you want things a bit thicker and more curried, toss in a cube or two more for the curry roux. Itâ€™s that easy! title: Visiting the MOST BEAUTIFUL Place on Earth! | The Azores
description: âœ… Click here to follow our family on INSTAGRAM, to see other photos and stories not published here! ğŸ‘‰ğŸ» http://instagram.com/mindymcknight|This trip is in our TOP 3 ALL-TIME travel destinations in the world, and we've been to over 50 countries! If you have never heard of the Azores islands (off the coast of Portugal), you need to put it near the top of your bucket list destinations... watch this video to see why!|When each of our kids graduate from high school, we take them on a senior trip anywhere they want, and get to pick a few friends to come along. Since Rylan just graduated, she chose to go to the Azores islands, off the coast of Portugal. I had done a ton of research beforehand, and wondered why I had never really heard of them before!|âœ… Shop my NEWLY LAUNCHED Hairitage hair care products, including heat styling tools and hair accessories, in stores exclusively at Walmart, or online HERE: ğŸ‘‰ğŸ» https://shopstyle.it/l/btxSQ  |The Azores have to be the most BEAUTIFUL place we have ever been, and that is saying a lot since I've been to 54 countries in my lifetime! I can only explain them as a mix of Kauai (Hawaii), Ireland, England, Switzerland, and New Zealand, all on just a few small islands. From small fishing villages along the coast, all the way to the craters of the volcanoes that created the islands, everything is FRAGRANT, LUSH, and GREEN! Even the sides of the roads and highways have naturally-growing hydrangea bushes that are in full bloom in the June-Aug months. The island has quite a moderate temperature year round, with lots of moisture due to its location in the Gulf Stream.|Rylan picked her friend Kelsey Leroy (@Kesley Jade) of the Leroy's, Kamri, and their friend Kara to come with her. She also agreed to let Brooklyn & Bailey with their significant others come along, if they wanted, so they did. We had to leave Dax and Paisley since Paisley was attending one of two summer camps and Daxton is a summer counselor for a local coding camp. We also found during research that the island had many dangerous sites that are not meant for younger kids (waterfall repelling, treacherous hikes, hot volcanic calderas, ocean hot pools, dangerous switchbacks, etc.) |All of the places we visited on the island are listed in the video. (Please be aware, that most rental cars on the island are manual transmission, meaning you have to be comfortable driving a stick shift and clutch. We were not quite prepared for how steep and winding some of the roads were!) The food was much less expensive than in the US, and all of the people we met were super nice and most speak excellent English.|We loved San Miguel so much that want to come back and explore the other islands! If you are looking for an adventurous travel destination that is in our TOP 3 all time, then put the Azores on your list! There are naturally occurring hot springs all over, tiny fisherman villages, stunning hikes, and you can even have a stew cooked right there on the volcano ground!|Please be sure to click the "ğŸ””" next to the SUBSCRIBE button, to join our Notification Squad for PowerHour each week, and leave a comment below telling me what you would like to see next!|â¤ï¸'s -Mindy|___|We post a new hairstyle tutorial or Behind the Braids family vlog every Monday afternoon {4pm CST}! |So, please don't forget to subscribe to our YouTube channel...|http://www.youtube.com/user/CuteGirlsHairstyles?sub_confirmation=1|You can also find me HERE!|   ğŸ“¸  Instagram | http://instagram.com/mindymcknight|   â°  TikTok: @mindymcknight|   ğŸ¥  Twitter | http://www.twitter.com/CuteGirlHair|   ğŸ‘¤  Facebook | http://www.facebook.com/CuteGirlsHairstyles|   ğŸ“Œ  Pinterest | http://www.pinterest.com/CGHairstyles| |How do you say "Hairstyles" in many of the world's top languages? title: How to Choose a Finish Nailer | Tool Lab | Ask This Old House
description: In this video, This Old House carpenter Nathan Gilbert explains everything you need to know about choosing a finish nailer for your trim and molding projects.|SUBSCRIBE to This Old House: http://bit.ly/SubscribeThisOldHouse.|In the latest installment of Tool Lab, Nathan Gilbert talks about nail guns. Nathan takes us through all of the most common finish nailers, from heavy-duty 15-gauge nailers to small headless 23-gauge pin nailers.|Finish Nailers Have Specific Purposes|Finish nailers are ideal for trimming windows and doors, hanging crown molding, or fastening delicate woodworking pieces. But the reality is that one nailer can't handle it all. Large nailers will split small pieces of trim, while small pin nailers won't have the holding power to keep a molding in place. For this reason, many DIYers and pros keep several types (and sizes) of finish nailers on hand.|The Difference is the Size of the Nails|There are several different types of finish nailers, each categorized by the size of the fastener they fire. The fastener sizes come in gauges, and the lower the gauge number, the larger or thicker the fastener.|* 15-Gauge nails are large and offer a lot of holding power. They're extremely effective for running base molding or hanging crown molding, but they do leave larger holes in the moldings.|* 16-Gauge nails are still large and offer a lot of holding power, but they're a bit more versatile than 15-gauge. These nails are great for trimming doors and other general carpentry tasks.|* 18-Gauge nails are smaller and thinner, and they have smaller heads than 15- or 16-gauge nails. This makes them useful for fastening small moldings or nailing the side of a molding to a window or door jamb.|* 23-Gauge nailers, or pin nailers, fire small headless pins. While they don't offer much holding power, they're helpful for delicate moldings, woodworking pieces, or mitered returns on window aprons and moldings. They're often used with glue.|Power Source|There are two nailer types: pneumatic and battery-powered. While both types will handle the same tasks, some distinct advantages and disadvantages exist.|Pneumatic nailers are typically lighter and less expensive to purchase. However, they require an additional compressor and an air hose to fire nails. They also require a bit more maintenance than a battery-powered model.|Battery-powered finish nailers are more expensive and heavier than pneumatic nailers. However, they don't require the user to lug an air compressor around, and there isn't a hose to trip over or keep the user tethered in place.|Where to find it?|When it comes to installing trim around windows, doors, baseboards, crown molding, assembling cabinet parts, or installing stair treads and risers, as you can see, one nail gun does not fit all. The most common and readily available types are 15 gauge, 16 gauge, 18 gauge, and 23 gauge. The difference between them is the gauge nail that they shoot. Nathan explains how to select a finish nailer and its standard features.|Looking for more step by step guidance on how to complete projects around the house? title: Rudy Giuliani, Lindsey Graham and John Eastman subpoenaed by Fulton County DA in election probe

title: Water crisis in Southern Europe: Severe droughts and scarce rain force water restrictions | DW News
description: Amplified by human-induced climate change and water over-consumption, southern Europeans are feeling the consequences of more extreme heat waves and longer droughts. Now governments from Portugal to Italy are calling on citizens to limit water use to the bare minimum. But in some places this is not enough. While private consumption of water in the EU accounts for just 9% of total usage, around 60% is absorbed by agriculture. |The situation is probably most dramatic in northern Italy, where the region is suffering its worst drought in 70 years. More than 100 cities have been called on to limit water consumption as much as possible. On Monday, the Italian government declared a state of emergency for five regions until the end of the year. It plans to provide â‚¬36 million ($37 million) in the short term to combat the water crisis.  Due to months of drought and scarce winter rain, the water levels of the Dora Baltea and Po â€” the largest river in Italy â€” are eight times lower than usual. Both rivers feed one of the most important agricultural regions in all of Europe, with 30% of production currently threatened by drought. The irrigation authority in the northwestern region around the Sesia river has already ordered that fruit trees and poplars no longer be watered. The saved water will be used to irrigate the economically important rice crop. |The mayor of the city of Verona has announced that watering gardens and sports fields, washing cars and patios, and filling pools and swimming pools is now prohibited until the end of August to safeguard drinking water supplies. Vegetable gardens may only be watered at night. Pisa is also resorting to rationing. As of this month drinking water can only be used "for domestic use and personal hygiene." Failure to comply will result in fines of up to 500 euros ($516). In Milan, meanwhile, all decorative water fountains have been turned off. The mayor of the small town of Castenaso wants to tackle the problem unconventionally: He has banned hairdressers and barbers from washing their customers' hair twice. There are 10 hairdressers in the small town of 16,000 inhabitants, with the measure aiming to save thousands of liters of water per day.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#drought #Italy #ClimateChange

title: Warga Papua Tengah Berunjuk Rasa, Minta DPR untuk Buat Timika Jadi Ibu Kota
description: KOMPAS.TV - Pemekaran wilayah ini mendapat dukungan penuh dari pemerintah pusat dan Dewan Perwakilan Rakyat (DPR), fokus pemekaran ini untuk kesejahteraan rakyat.||||Sementara itu di Mimika, Papua, sejumlah warga berjalan kaki dari eks Pasar Swadaya Timika, menuju Kantor DPRD Mimika, Papua,||||Warga meminta kepada DPR RI, untuk menetapkan Timika sebagai ibu kota Provinsi Papua Tengah.||||Menurut warga, timika sangat layak menjadi ibu kota provinsi Papua Tengah yang akan ditetapkan DPR RI ||||Ya, Dewan Perwakilan Rakyat (DPR) akhirnya mengesahkan tiga provinsi baru di Papua, yakni provinsi Papua Selatan, provinsi Papua Tengah, dan provinsi Papua Pegunungan.||||Diharapkan pemekaran ini mendorong dan meningkatkan pembangunan di bumi Papua||||Pengesahan ini menjadi angin segar bagi masyarakat asli Papua, karena pemekaran ini akan menjadi modal utama untuk membuka lapangan kerja baru.||||Diharapkan, pemekaran ini dapat menyerap 80 persen pekerja dari orang asli papua.||||Selain tenaga kerja, pemekaran juga bertujuan menarik investasi ke bumi Papua.||||Pengesahan pemekaran wilayah di papua menegaskan, bahwa pemerintah serius dalam membangun Papua dengan memberikan otonomi khusus pemekaran yang bertujuan untuk peningkatan ekonomi wilayah.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306220/warga-papua-tengah-berunjuk-rasa-minta-dpr-untuk-buat-timika-jadi-ibu-kota

title: Sloviansk reports heavy shelling, Donetsk governor calls for evacuation of civilians |Ukraine latest
description: A day after Russia claimed control of the Luhansk region, Pavlo Kyrylenko, the governor of Donetsk province in eastern Ukraine, has urged the evacuation of 350,000 people. Kyrylenko said that this would be a necessary step to save lives and allow Ukrainian forces to prepare defenses in towns ahead of a Russian advance. "The destiny of the whole country will be decided by the Donetsk region," Kyrylenko told reporters and added â€œOnce there are less people, we will be able to concentrate more on our enemy and perform our main tasks.'' The comments from the governor come as Russian forces bombarded the key city of Sloviansk.|Regional authorities in Donetsk said two were killed and seven more were injured during heavy shelling on the Ukrainian city of Sloviansk on Tuesday. Local governor Pavlo Kyrylenko made the announcement on Telegram and said Russian shells had targeted the city's market. AFP journalists in Sloviansk reportedly saw the marketplace hit as firefighters worked to put out the fire while three shells hit nearby streets. "Once again the Russians are intentionally targeting places where civilians assemble," Kyrylenko wrote. In 2014, Sloviansk was briefly controlled by Russian-backed forces before Ukraine could retake the city.|With Russia now expected to turn its attention to the city of Sloviansk in the Donetsk region following the capture of Lysychansk, foreign and security policy analyst Domitilla Sagramoso told DW that despite these developments, Russia has made limited progress in the rest of the Donetsk Oblast, and pointed to the defensive efforts of Ukrainian forces.|"There have been hardly any advances of Russian forces in the rest of the Donetsk Oblast. So so far they've been really very good at holding any Russian attack. They have very good defensive positions, so one could expect that for some time these regions might not fall." Sagromoso said that Russian forces may feel like they have momentum and are expected to target Sloviansk but she highlighted Ukraineâ€™s ability to launch attacks on Russian targets in hit and run attacks. "It's also important to note how much the Ukrainians are also hitting behind the lines. There have been attacks on ammunition depots, on infrastructure, on airports in the areas of Melitopol, also in Kharkiv Oblast, also in Donetsk Oblast."|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #Donbas

title: Police search for a motive in Highland Park mass shooting
description: A seventh person has died from the mass shooting in Highland Park, Illinois. Police said today the gunman pre-planned the July Fourth attack for several weeks. More than 30 other people were injured after the suspect fired over 70 rounds during a holiday parade. While the community grieves, law enforcement is still trying to determine a motive. title: Bodycam Shows Police Officer Saving 3-Year-Old Choking On Quarter
description: Bodycam video shows an Oklahoma deputy saving a 3-year-old boy who was choking on a quarter on June 7, 2018. The mother waved the officer down at a car wash after realizing her son was choking on something. The officer pounded on the boy's back multiple times until a quarter popped out of his mouth. Season 4 of 'Stranger Things' is streaming on Netflix.

title: How to Alter the Perception of Mental Health Care in Russia | Olga Kitaina | TED
description: During the Soviet Union era, therapy was often used as a tool of political oppression. Since then, Russia has seen major reforms in mental health care -- but stigmas and distrust for the practice still live on. title: Eagles ranked as most talented team in NFC East, ahead of Dak Prescott & Cowboys | NFL | UNDISPUTED

title: How Kevin Durant's request impacts the league's mobility, Devin Booker-KD duo? | NBA | THE HERD
description: Kevin Durant remains with the Brooklyn Nets after requesting a trade last week .. for now. Reports do not rule out a KD-Golden State Warriors reunion. With many superstars leaving multiple teams to join newer squads, this brings up the question on mobility in the NBA. Players want more leverage but often do not end up as champions (ex: Kyrie Irving in Boston, James Harden's stops). Colin Cowherd breaks down why he believes this is not 'great' for the players. KD listed the Phoenix Suns as his top destination next to the Miami Heat. A report says that the Suns are engaging with the Nets about a trade but not rushing it. title: RETRO EVs: Honda e Advance vs Fiat 500 Electric | Stig's Garage ft. Becky Evans
description: Electrification is clearly the future for small city runarounds. However, some manufacturers are looking to the past for design cues - in a good way...|The Honda e has dinky dimensions and doe eyes, reminiscent of its 80s ancestor, the Honda City. Underneath its retro exterior, it has a 35.5kWh battery and an electric motor that produces 152bhp. The Fiat 500 Electric looks like... well, a Fiat 500 - a tried and tested shape which has barely changed since the 50s. It doesn't have as much power as its Japanese rival (116bhp) but it does come in almost 200kgs lighter.|These arent The Stig's standard track weapons of choice, but they should make for an interesting race. title: Jaishankar accuses 'Delhi media' of bias before 2014; Praises  PM Modi as 'national leader'
description: External Affairs Minister S Jaishankar praised Prime Minister Narendra Modi, and said that he has captured the sentiments and aspirations of the entire country. Speaking at an event on book Modi@20: Dreams meet delivery, in New Delhi. Jaishankar said that before 2014, the "Delhi media" used to bestow the status of "national leader" on all its "friends and favourites". The book, 'Modi@20 Dreams Meet Delivery', was launched by Vice President Venkaiah Naidu last month and is an anthology about Prime Minister Narendra Modi. Watch this video for more.|#india #pmmodi #jaishankar #modi #modigovernment #bjp #politics

title: Dugaan Penyelewengan Dana Donasi ACT, Pengamat: Bisa Masuk Ranah Pidana!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Dugaan penyelewengan dana bantuan kemanusiaan dari masyarakat yang dikumpulkan Aksi Cepat Tanggap atau ACT diungkap Majalah Tempo.||||Dalam laporannya, Majalah Tempo menyebut adanya biaya operasional yang terlalu besar yang digunakan hingga penyaluran bantuan yang dianggap tidak sesuai.||||Fasilitas dan gaji petinggi aksi cepat tanggap juga dianggap fantastis. Berdasarkan laporan Majalah Tempo yang didasarkan dari keterangan sejumlah staf dan mantan petinggi ACT gaji petinggi aksi cepat tanggap jumlahnya fantastis.||||Untuk tingkat ketua dewan pembina mendapat gaji Rp 250 juta per bulan,||tingkat senior vice president senilai Rp 150 juta perbulan, vice president Rp 80 juta rupiah per bulan dan direktur Rp 50 juta.||||Menanggapi dugaan penyelewengan yang menyebabkan krisis keuangan ACT dibantah oleh presiden aksi cepat tanggap. ACT juga mengaku telah melakukan perbaikan soal besaran gaji petinggi.||||Terlepas dari dugaan penyelewengan yang diungkap Tempo, lembaga kemanusiaan sepatutnya menjaga transparansi dari setiap dana kemanusiaan yang dikumpulkan.||||Benarkah dugaan penyeleweangan dana kemanusiaan ini bisa masuk ranah pidana kami membahasnya bersama, Direktur Pencegahan Badan Nasional Penanggulangan Terorisme  Ahmad Nurwakhid, Pengamat Hukum Pidana Universitas Trisakti Asep Iwan Iriawan, dan Ketua Komunitas Warung Tegal Nusantara Mukroni. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306168/dugaan-penyelewengan-dana-donasi-act-pengamat-bisa-masuk-ranah-pidana

title: AWESOME GADGETS AND TOOLS FOR ANY SITUATION | Kitchen, Cleaning And Camping
description: Hi there! Sometimes we can't imagine our lives without laptops and other devices. However, can daily routine be any better? YES! If you don't have a dishwasher, forget about that idea, you barely need one. Use kitchen sink shower to wash your dishes! Do you remember marshmallow smores? We feel it! Grab this fantastic gadget that melts marshmallow and chocolate at home! No fire needed :)||Are you struggling with pizza cutting? Party is going on, friends are waiting and pizza is not even cut. title: 'Kali is alcohol-accepting Goddess': Mahua Moitra sparks fury; TMC condemns, BJP demands arrest
description: TMC Lok Sabha MP Mahua Moitra has sparked fury with her description of Goddess Kali amid ongoing row over the deity's smoking poster. The TMC MP while speaking at India Today Conlave East said that she believes Kali is a meat-eating, alcohol-accepting Goddess. title: How does alcohol cause hangovers? - Judy Grisel
description: Discover how alcohol impacts your bodyâ€™s processes and causes hangovers, and find out what causes the most common hangover symptoms.|--|The molecule responsible for hangovers is ethanol, which we colloquially refer to as alcohol. Ethanol is present in all alcoholic beverages, and generally speaking, the more ethanol, the greater the potential for a hangover. So, how exactly does alcohol cause a hangoverâ€” and is there any way to prevent one? title: Claressa Shields & Savannah Marshall With the Most Intense Faceoff | #ShieldsMarshall Sept 10 ESPN+
description: Watch the intense faceoff from todays press conference with #ClaressaShields & #SavannahMarshall #ShieldsMarshall will be live and exclusive on Sept 10 on ESPN+|Two heated rivalries will come to a head Saturday, Sept. 10 in a historic championship doubleheader at the O2 Arena in London.| |The previously announced main event will see two-time Olympic gold medalist Claressa Shields, the WBC/WBA/IBF/Ring Magazine middleweight champion, aim to once again become undisputed at 160 pounds by facing longtime rival and WBO titleholder Savannah Marshall.| |Shields and Marshall faced off as amateurs, with Marshall edging Shields by decision at the 2012 AIBA Womenâ€™s World Championships in Qinhuangdao, China. Shields went 77-1 as an amateur and is the only female boxer to win undisputed titles in two weight classes.| |In the co-feature, Mikaela Mayer will look to get one step closer to becoming the first undisputed champ in her division by putting her WBO/IBF/Ring Magazine junior lightweight titles on the line against WBC champion Alycia Baumgardner.| |A total of seven world titles and two Ring Magazine belts will be on the line.| |Promoted by Salita Promotions and Boxxer, in association with Top Rank, Shields-Marshall, Mayer-Baumgardner, and undercard bouts will stream live and exclusively in the U.S. on ESPN+|Try ESPN+ For Free: https://watch.espnplus.com/toprank/|Subscribe to our YouTube channel to get notified about the latest highlights, free full fights, and fight week content as it's posted.|Follow Top Rank on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/trboxing|Follow Top Rank on Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/toprank|Like Top Rank on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/trboxing

title: Thor: Love and Thunder Review
description: Thor: Love and Thunder debuts in theaters on July 8, 2022. Review by Tom Jorgensen.||||Thor: Love and Thunder is largely successful in honoring Thor's long journey towards self-actualization and rarely falters while keying into the crackling chemistry between leads Chris Hemsworth, Natalie Portman, and Tessa Thompson. It's essentially the MCU's first romantic comedy, and plays with those tropes in delightful ways. But while Thor and Jane's relationship is handled well, Love and Thunder is less deft -- and a lot safer than you'd expect -- in pushing the greater MCU story forward. Christian Bale's Gorr feels underutilized and Tessa Thompson's King Valkyrie takes a frustrating back seat, especially as the movie goes on. Taika Waititi's signature humor and visual style persist from Ragnarok, and are essential to buoying the movie through its cookie-cutter plot. With Hemsworth as enthusiastic an Asgardian as ever, Thor's future with both love and thunder are bright.|#IGN #Movies #Thor

title: This Rugged Speaker is made from.... Silk?
description: When I hear the material 'Silk' I don't automatically think of 'speaker' But it sounds GOOD! Grab your Motion Boom Plus from Soundcore HERE: https://soundcore.club/JREMotionBoomPlus huge thanks to Soundcore for sponsoring this video. title: Why Delhi-Dubai SpiceJet flight landed at Karachi Airport? The Full Story
description: A Spicejet flight from Delhi to Dubai landed in Pakistan's Karachi after it developed a techinical snag mid-air. Spicejet in its statement said that flight SG-11 diverted to Karachi following a snag in its light indicator. The DGCA has begun a probe and said in a statement that the 'crew observed an unusual reduction in fuel quantity from the left tank, following which aircraft diverted to Karachi in coordination with ATC'. This is the 4th incident that the budget airline has witnessed in the last 3 weeks. Watch this video to know more.|#Spicejet #DelhiDubaiFlight #Karachi #Pakistan #Emergency #DirectorGeneralOfCivilAviation #DGCA #JyotiradityaScindia #TechnicalSnag

title: Taliban to approach Modi govt to facilitate Afghan students' return to India
description: Afghanistan's Taliban government will approach India's Narendra Modi government to facilitate the return of Afghan students back to India to resume their studies. This after a delegation of Afghan students met foreign minister Amir Khan Muttaqi in Kabul and sought his help in this regard. The students had returned to their home country after the outbreak of coronavirus in 2020. Watch the video for more.|#india #afghanistan #taliban #amirkhanmuttaqi #bjp #narendramodi #pmmodi #kabul #taliban

title: PPATK Paparkan Temuannya untuk Dugaan Pelanggaran Donasi ACT
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Aksi Cepat Tanggap, Ibnu Khajar mengakui ada pemotongan sebesar 13,7 persen dari total uang donasi yang diperoleh per tahun.||||Ibnu Khajar mengatakan, pemotongan untuk operasional termasuk membayar gaji karyawan dan petinggi ACT.||||Namun||||Pusat Pelaporan dan Analisis Transaksi  atau||||PPATK dalam rilisnya meminta masyarakat lebih bijak berdonasi.||||Kepala PPATK, Ivan Yustiavandana mengatakan ada indikasi dugaan penyelewengan penggunaan dana yang diterima masyarakat dan pihak lain.||||Ada beberapa transaksi yang patut diduga terkait dengan kegiatan kegiatan yang melanggar peraturan perundangan.||||Seperti apa temuan PPATK untuk dugaan adanya penyelewengan dana organisasi Aksi Cepat Tanggapa atau ACT?||||Telah terhubung melalui telepon Kepala Pusat Pelaporan dan Analisis Transaksi atau PPATK, Ivan Yustiavandana. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306167/ppatk-paparkan-temuannya-untuk-dugaan-pelanggaran-donasi-act

title: Cruz vs Vargas FULL FIGHT: June 19, 2021 | PBC on Showtime
description: (June 19, 2021) Isaac "Pitbull" Cruz improved to 22-1-1 (15 KOs) following his nonstop dominating unanimous decision victory over Francisco Vargas in their 10-round lightweight bout live on SHOWTIME.|A highly anticipated battle between power-punching Mexico City natives, 23-year-old top lightweight contender Isaac Cruz (22-1-1, 15 KOs) scored a wide unanimous decision over former champion Francisco Vargas (27-3-2, 19 KOs). The official scores were 100-89, 99-90 and 97-92.|Cruz, who shot up the lightweight rankings in 2020 and punctuated his year with an electrifying first-round knockout over Diego Magdaleno in September, came out early looking for a similar result. Cruz continued to throw power punches, including his signature overhand right, but Vargas was able to avoid any devastating blows. It was the 36-year-old Vargas who was the more active fighter, throwing 586 punches compared to Cruzâ€™s 548. However, Cruz out-landed Vargas 188-148 and landed 43 percent of his power shots en route to the victory.|Cruz consistently led with his head, resulting in a number of head clashes, including in the eventful 10th and final round which led to a significant cut over Vargasâ€™ right eye that the Mexican warrior fought through. In the final minute of the fight, Cruz sent Vargas to the canvas for just the second time in his career with a barrage of punches, topping off an impressive performance.|#IsaacCruz #FranciscoVargas #CruzVargas|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: Monthly update of activity at Yellowstone Volcano for July 2022
description: Mike Poland, scientist-in-charge of the Yellowstone Volcano Observatory, describes activity at Yellowstone volcano in this monthly update for July 1, 2022. |The Yellowstone region saw record flooding owing to heavy rainfall and snowmelt during June 10â€“13.  Several roads and bridges were washed out, and many small landslides and rockfalls occurred, especially in the northern part of Yellowstone National Park.  Although severe, the flooding is not expected to have any significant impact on seismic or hydrothermal activity in the Yellowstone region.  The only potential impact would be on geyser activity, because some geysers tend to erupt slightly more frequently during high-precipitation years compared to drier years.  The timing shift is subtle but statistically significant. |There were 149 located earthquakes in June (maximum magnitude M2.4) and several small swarms. There was continued caldera subsidence and slight subsidence at Norris. Steamboat Geyser had two major water eruptions, on June 10 and 20. |For questions, email yvowebteam@usgs.gov|Video: https://www.usgs.gov/media/videos/monthly-update-activity-yellowstone-volcano-july-2021-0

title: 'Indelible scar...': 117 ex-judges, officials pen open letter; Criticize SC comments on Nupur Sharma
description: 15 former judges, 77 former bureaucrats and 25 retired officers of the armed forces have criticised the Supreme Court's recent comments against former BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma, whose remarks on Prophet Mohammed led to protests and a diplomatic row. Their open letter tweeted by ANI, says the two-judge bench's observation that Nupur is â€œsingle-handedly responsible for what is happening in the countryâ€ was a â€œvirtual exoneration of the dastardliest beheading at Udaipurâ€. The open letter issued today says those â€œunfortunate and unprecedented commentsâ€ from the bench of Justice Surya Kant and Justice JB Pardiwala â€œare not in sync with judicial ethos.â€ Watch this video for more details.|#nupursharma #supremecourt #openletter #armedforces #judges #lawyers #prophetinsult #prophetmuhammad #bjp #india #remarks #comment

title: Saat Megawati Kaget Prabowo Beri Hormat di HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara
description: SEMARANG, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah momen di saat Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto memberi hormat kepada Ketum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri yang terlihat kaget dan tertawa mendapatkan sapaan dari Prabowo Subianto.||||Prabowo dan Megawati hadir dan duduk berdampingan di HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara pada 5 Juli 2022.||||HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara ini diselenggarakan di Semarang, Jawa Tengah.||||Baca Juga Prabowo Puji Keberhasilan Pemerintahan Jokowi di Berbagai Bidang saat Beri Kuliah Umum di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305492/prabowo-puji-keberhasilan-pemerintahan-jokowi-di-berbagai-bidang-saat-beri-kuliah-umum||||Sementara itu, Presiden Jokowi menjadi inspektur upacara di Peringatan HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara di Akademi Kepolisian Semarang, Jawa Tengah.||||Peringatan HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara ini dilangsungkan pada Selasa, 5 Juli 2022.||||Video Editor: : Lintang||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306018/saat-megawati-kaget-prabowo-beri-hormat-di-hut-ke-76-bhayangkara

Fish or meat-based fry recipes have always been popular snacks across India. title: Uddhav challenges Maha CM Eknath for mid-term polls; Sena accuses BJP of â€˜stealing majority'
description: The Uddhav Thackeray faction has cried foul after Maharashtra CM eknath Shinde's floor test victory. Through its mouthpiece Saamna, Sena termed Eknath's victory as stolen majority. Separately, Uddhav Thackeray even challenged Eknath Shinde for early mid-term polls. Quoting Uddhav at a meet of district presidents on Monday, PTI reported, â€œThis is BJP's ploy to end the Shiv Sena. Instead of playing all these games, we will go to the court of people. If we are wrong, people of the state will send us home. title: Momen Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Tawaf di Masjidil Haram, Diabadikan Penceramah Gus Miftah
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil dan sang istri Atalia tengah jalani rangkaian umrah dan haji di Arab Saudi.||||Hal tersebut juga terekam dalam unggahan penceramah Gus Miftah di Instagram.||||Sebuah video memperlihatkan kebersamaan Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia sedang bertawaf di Masjidil Haram, Mekkah.||||Baca Juga Sejumlah Gerai Holywings Ditutup, Ridwan Kamil: Langgar Aturan, Ada Konsekuensinya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/306054/sejumlah-gerai-holywings-ditutup-ridwan-kamil-langgar-aturan-ada-konsekuensinya||||Nampak keduanya rapi mengenangkan baju ihram, sebagai mana yang biasa dipakai oleh jemaah haji.||||Ridwan Kamil berangkat haji karena ditugaskan memimpin belasan ribu jemaah calon haji asal Jawa Barat.||||Ia berangkat sebagai Amirul Hajj, yang bertiugas memastikan kelancaran dan kemanan peserta atau jemaah haji asal Jabar.||||Dalam sebuah kesempatan, Ridwan Kamil meminta maaf karena tahun ini hanya 45 persen dari total kuota jemaah haji Jawa Barat yang bisa berangkat.||||Ia meminta calon jemaah yang belum bisa berangkat tahun ini agar bersabar menunggu kesempatan berikutnya.||||Ridwan Kamil juga meniatkan berhaji atas nama sang anak, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||RK mengaku telah berpamitan sekaligus berziarah ke makam Eril di Cimaung, Kab. Bandung.||||"Sekalian di momen ini, saya akan berhaji atas nama almarhum Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz. Karenanya, tadi pagi ziarah, pamit dan berdoa di makam Eril."||||"Mohon doanya dari semua agar diberi kelancaran dan seluruh jemaah haji Jawa Barat dan Indonesia lancar dan sehat selamat kembali ke tanah air sebagai Haji mabrur dan Hajjah mabrurah. Aamiin."||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306068/momen-ridwan-kamil-dan-atalia-tawaf-di-masjidil-haram-diabadikan-penceramah-gus-miftah

title: Neon White Review
description: Reviewed by Luke Reilly on PC. Also available on Nintendo Switch.||||"Neon White is a quick and compulsive first-person platformer that's surprisingly simple to understand and play, but packs a very stern speedrunning challenge at its core. Tying your combat options to your traversal mechanics, Neon White makes every encounter a deadly parkour puzzle that can be replayed over and over, in search of the perfect run and the tightest time. The dialogue between its unlikeable troupe of angst-ridden, anime-inspired assassins may be a hokey misstep, but its airtight level design and fantastic sense of momentum ensure Neon White's gameplay is something to celebrate."

title: Rahul fake news: Anchor Rohit Ranjanâ€™s detention sparks UP versus Chhattisgarh police fight
description: Zee News anchor Rohit Ranjan has been detained by the Noida police after he ran a misleading video clip of Rahul Gandhi. He was detained by Noida police this morning after Chhattisgarh cops reached his house to arrest him. He informed Yogi Adityanath & Ghaziabad police via Twitter about Chhattisgarh police's entry. This sparked a massive state police war. On July 1, Rohit in his show ran a misleading clip of Rahul Gandhi linking it to Udaipur's tailor Kanhaiya Lal's murder. After the row, Zee News had apologised for running wrong content. title: How U.S. I-Day parade turned into 'warzone'; Shooter Crimo unleashed AR-15 in Chicago Suburb
description: It was the morning of the U.S. Independence Day Parade celebration for a Chicago suburb when suddenly dozens of bullets were fired, followed by chaos in the streets amid screams. It was at this moment, when 22-year-old Robert Crimo opened fire at the crowd from a rooftop with his AR-15. He was arrested later after hours of manhunt. 6 people died and at least 80 others were injured in the mass shooting, including kids. One of the clips, which is particularly disturbing, captures the moment when the attacker opened fire from a rooftop. People ran in all directions, seeking shelter, and teens - on bicycles - could not understand what was happening. Watch this video for more details.|#unitedstates #massshooting #july4th #illinois #july4 #chicago #independeceday #ar15 #shootout

title: Norway: After burning Quran, anti-Islamist Lars Thorsenâ€™s car rammed; Dramatic chase on cam
description: Norway's anti-Islam extremist group leader Lars Thorsen was caught in a dramatic car chase and collision after burning Islam's Holy book Quran on the outskirts of Oslo. The video shows Thorsen & his group burning Quran in a largely Muslim-dominated neighbourhood. Soon, locals gathered and pushed them back while trying to douse the fire. They were then chased by a car which rammed into them on the highway. Watch this video to know more.|#Norway #AntiIslamExtremist #LarsThorsen #Quran #Muslims #HolyBook #Oslo #Terrorism

title: On Camera, Sidhu Moose Wala Shooters Seen Waving Guns, Celebrating In Car
description: The killers of singer Sidhu Moose Wala are seen celebrating with their weapons, apparently after the crime, in a set of videos found on the phone of one of the shooters. The five men in a car, all of them smiling, are seen flaunting their guns at the camera as Punjabi music blared in the background. Two videos, celebrating the murder, emerged after the phone of the youngest of the shooters, Ankit Sirsa, was scanned. title: Tak Punya Smartphone, Sopir Angkot Bingung Beli BBM dengan Aplikasi Mypertamina
description: INDRAMAYU, KOMPAS.TV - Tidak punya ponsel pintar, para sopir angkot tolak beli BBM pakai aplikasi atau website Mypertamina.||||Para sopir angkot di Indramayu ini misalnya, menolak penggunanaan Mypertamina.||||Mereka mengaku berat dan ribet jika harus beli pertalite dan solar dengan Mypetamina.||||Para sopir bingung lantaran tidak punya ponsel pintar mumpuni untuk mengikuti ketentuan Pertamina.||||Sebelumnya, pihak Pertamina menjelaskan skema beli BBM lewat Mypertamina agar penyaluran subsidi BBM tepat sasaran.||||Pasalnya selama ini, 60 persen masyarakat yang menggunakan BBM subsidi adalah golongan masyarakat yang mampu. Alias tidak tepat saaran.||||Penerapan penggunaan Mypertamina untuk membeli pertalite dan solar yang dimulai 1 Juli lalu langsung menuai banyak respon.||||Uji coba awal dilakukan di beberapa kota/kabupaten yang tersebar di 5 Provinsi antara lain Sumatera Barat, Kalimantan Selatan, Sulawesi Utara, Jawa Barat, dan di Yogyakarta. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305856/tak-punya-smartphone-sopir-angkot-bingung-beli-bbm-dengan-aplikasi-mypertamina

title: On Cam: Racist slurs hurled at Indian fans during Ind-Eng match at Edgbaston; ECB vows probe
description: Indian fans were subjected to racial abuse during the India-England 4th test match in Edgbaston. This incident came to light after some of the fans took to Twitter and posted photos and videos of the incident. They also claimed that no action was taken despite complaining to the steward about the incident. Meanwhile, the England Cricket Board, reacting to the tweets, apologised for the incident and promised a probe. Edgbaston stadium's chief executive also issued a statement condemning the incident. Watch this video to know more.|#Racism #India #England #Edgbaston #RacialSlur #Abuse #IndianFans #EnglandCricketBoard #Apology

title: UP: Man who sold chicken on paper with Hindu deities, attacks cops with knife before arrest
description: A Muslim roadside restaurant owner has been arrested in Uttar Pradeshâ€™s Sambhal district for wrapping chicken in a newspaper carrying images of Hindu deities. As per police FIR, when a police team reached his shop, Talib Hussain attacked them with a knife with an intention to kill. He has been booked under IPC Sections 153-A (promoting enmity between different groups on grounds of religion, race, place of birth, residence), 295A (deliberate and malicious acts, intended to outrage religious feelings of any class by insulting its religion or religious beliefs) and 307 (attempt to murder). Workers at the restaurant insisted wrapping food items in newspapers is a common practice and Talib did not do this to hurt anyone. They added it was just a matter of chance that Talib used a newspaper carrying images of Hindu gods and goddesses. Watch this video for more details.|#muslim #chicken #uttarpradesh #sambhal #religion #religious #uppolice

title: Australian Sikh soldiers at Khalistan event, British Army delegation in Pak raise eyebrows in India
description: India is irked by the recent visits of British & Australian Armies' Sikh delegations to controversial events. A twelve-member Sikh delegation of the British Army visited historical & religious sites in Pakistan on June 28 at the invitation of Pakistan Army chief General Qamar Bajwa. In another case, an Australian Army Sikh delegation was spotted at a pro-Khalistan event in New South Wales. However, the Australian Defence forces distanced itself from the visit of its Sikh contingent. Watch this video to know more.|#India #Pakistan #Australia #Army #SikhDelegation #Khalistan #Bajwa #BritishArmy #AustralianArmy

title: Maryna Viazovska is awarded the 2022 Fields Medal
description: Maryna Viazovska has received a Fields Medal, a prestigious honor often described as the Nobel Prize of Mathematics, for her work on the sphere-packing problem in 8 and 24 dimensions. Previously, the problem had been solved for only three dimensions or fewer. Another Fields Medal is awarded to University of Geneva mathematician Hugo Duminil-Copin.|Read more: https://actu.epfl.ch/news/an-epfl-mathematician-is-awarded-a-fields-medal|Article en franÃ§ais: https://actu.epfl.ch/news/une-mathematicienne-de-l-epfl-recoit-la-medaille-f|EPFL press kit: https://go.epfl.ch/Fields2022|Chair of Number Theory : https://www.epfl.ch/labs/tn/|EPFL: https://www.epfl.ch/|#mathematics #Fieldsmedal #spherepacking

title: China prepares to give US$140 million parliament building to Zimbabwe
description: Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: |https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube|China is preparing to give Zimbabwe a new US$140 million building that will be home to the African nationâ€™s parliament. The gift is the latest in a series of grand projects across Africa that are designed to deepen Beijingâ€™s influence on the continent where China is already the largest trading partner and lender. The site at Mount Hampden, about 18km (11 miles) northwest of Zimbabweâ€™s capital Harare, heralds the start of a new city. The 650-seat building will replace the current colonial-era structure which has only 100 seats for Zimbabweâ€™s 350 legislators. The new parliament built by Chinaâ€™s Shanghai Construction Group was fully paid for by Beijing. It took 42 months to complete after a 10-month delay caused by Covid-19 disruptions.|Support us:|https://subscribe.scmp.com|Follow us on:|Website:  https://www.scmp.com|Facebook:  https://facebook.com/scmp|Twitter:  https://twitter.com/scmpnews|Instagram:  https://instagram.com/scmpnews|Linkedin:  https://www.linkedin.com/company/south-china-morning-post/|#scmp #World #Zimbabwe

title: Lifeguard Bit By Shark While Mimicking Distressed Swimmer During Training Exercise
description: Beaches along Nassau County re-opened, but with an urgent message of caution after 33-year-old lifeguard, Zack Gallo was attacked by a shark. Gallo was mimicking a swimmer in distress as part of a training exercise. Records dating back almost 200 years show shark attacks are rare, with most happening around popular surfing beaches like New Smyrna, Florida, where another shark bite occurred yesterday. title: India slams 'disrespect' to Goddess Kali in Canada; Indian HC in Ottawa seeks withdrawal of poster
description: India has asked Canada to withdraw the 'disrespectful' depiction of goddess Kali smoking in a film poster. The Indian High Commission in Ottawa urged Canadian authorities to withdraw 'provocative material'. This is after the Hindu community members accused the filmmaker of disrespecting Hindu gods. Back home, the poster has sparked massive outrage with Hindu groups slamming the filmmaker. title: What to do if hotels and restaurants levy Service Charge on your bills? All you need to know
description: Amid rising consumer complaints, the Central Consumer Protection Authority (CCPA) has barred hotels and restaurants from levying service charge automatically or by default in food bills and allowed customers to file complaints in case of violation. If any consumer finds that a hotel or restaurant is levying service charge in violation of the guidelines, s/he can request the concerned establishment to remove it from the bill amount. Watch this explainer for full information.|#Hotels #ServiceCharge #Restaurants #Guidelines #CentralConsumerProtectionAuthority #Bill #FoodBill

title: 'Forced to apologise':  How Nupur backers were threatened in Amravati over Prophet insult

title: Chinese Salt and Pepper [Anything]
description: Salt and pepper dishes! Probably the most internationally famous are the Cantonese sort of these, but they're a style that you can see throughout the country.|0:00 â€“ What is salt and pepper seasoning? |1:57 â€“ Version 1, salt and Sichuan pepper seasoning|2:59 â€“ Version 2, salt and white pepper seasoning|3:35 â€“ How to salt and pepper anything|4:17 â€“ Salt and pepper mushrooms|5:45 â€“ Salt and pepper ribs|7:21 â€“ Community Sponsor, Mutclord Whetstones|8:18 â€“ Other salt and pepper mixes?|MUTCLORD WHETSTONES|Link is here, be sure to click the coupon to get 15% off:|https://www.amazon.com/Diamond-Whetstone-Knife-Wet-stone-Sharpening-Stone/dp/B09TJKKV7C?maas=maas_adg_75A28F967A8BA2217688000891377D1A_afap_abs&ref_=aa_maas&tag=maas&th=1|HOW TO MAKE THE SALT & PEPPER MIX|* Whole Sichuan peppercorns (èŠ±æ¤’) -or- white peppercorns (ç™½èƒ¡æ¤’), ~1/2 tbsp|* Salt, ~1/2 tsp|* MSG (å‘³ç²¾), 1/4 tsp|Over a medium-low flame, toast the peppercorns for about three minutes until fragrant (and if using Sichuan peppercorns, until the peppercorns have a slight oily sheen to them). Transfer to a mortar, pound into a powder. Pass the powder through a fine mesh sieve to catch the bits that aren't broken down enough - you should have about 1 tsp of powder in the end.|Toast the salt and also pound that into a powder. If your MSG is the sort that's larger crystals, also pound that into a powder as well.|The final ratio of the mix will be 1 tsp toasted and pounded peppercorns, 1/2 tsp toasted and pounded salt, and 1/4 tsp MSG.|SALT & PEPPER MUSHROOMS|This dish is originally a Sichuan dish, and goes great with the Sichuan peppercorn version of the salt & pepper mix. |* Oyster mushrooms, 500g|* To marinate: salt, 1/4 tsp; sugar, 1/2 tsp; soy sauce (ç”ŸæŠ½), 1/2 tsp|* Starch coating: cornstarch (ç‰ç±³ç”Ÿç²‰), ~3 tbsp and rice flour (ç²˜ç±³ç²‰), ~3 tbsp (the rice flour can be subbed with additional cornstarch)|* Oil, for deep frying|* Salt & pepper seasoning from above (it should be ~1.75 tsp)|Wash your mushrooms, then blanch for about three minutes. Remove, let them cool down. Once they're cool enough to handle, squeeze out the liquid that's in the mushrooms. Pat dry. Mix with the ingredients from the marinade.|Immediately before frying, mix the mushrooms with the starch. Get a wok of oil up to ~180C (or until bubbles are rapidly forming around a pair of chopsticks), and drop the mushrooms in one by one. Fry until they've released their moisture and feel obviously 'hard' if you pulled a pair of chopsticks through them, ~7 minutes.|Remove the oil from the wok. Wipe with a paper towel. Over a medium-low flame, combine the mushrooms with the salt & pepper seasoning in the wok. |SALT & PEPPER RIBS|This dish is originally a Cantonese dish, and goes great with the white peppercorn version of the salt & pepper mix.|* Pork ribs, cut into ~2 inch sections, 1kg|* For the alkaline soak: sodium carbonate (ç¢±é¢) -or- kansui (æ§æ°´), 1 tsp; enough water to submerge the ribs|* To marinate: salt, 1/2 tbsp; soy sauce (ç”ŸæŠ½), 1/2 tbsp; liaojiu a.k.a. Shaoxing wine (æ–™é…’/ç»é…’), 1/2 tbsp|* Starch coating: cornstarch (ç‰ç±³ç”Ÿç²‰), ~3 tbsp and rice flour (ç²˜ç±³ç²‰), ~3 tbsp (the rice flour can be subbed with additional cornstarch)|* Oil, for deep frying|* Garlic, 1 clove, minced|* Salt & pepper seasoning from above (it should be ~1.75 tsp)|* Optional: mild chilis -or- bell pepper, mix of green and red (for looks)|Soak the ribs with the alkaline solution for one hour. Then drain, and leave the ribs running under a trickle of running water for 5-10 minutes, jostling every so often.|Remove the ribs, and move to a towel/rag. An old t-shirt is perfect. Wrap the ribs and *really* make sure you've dried them out. I like to also pat dry with a paper towel for good measure. Transfer to a bowl, marinate the ribs.|Immediately before frying, coat the ribs with the starch. Fry the ribs at 145C for about 5 minutes, or until a chopstick can poke through. Remove, crank the temperature to ~195C, give a second fry for ~30 seconds.|Remove the oil, wipe down the wok. Medium low flame, fry the garlic until fragrant. Add the ribs, mix. Add the seasoning, mix. Add the optional chilis, mix.|SICHUAN PEPPERCORN SOURCING|In this video we used quality Sichuan peppercorns - often the ones exported to the west can be seed-y, stem-y, and generally a little sad. title: How Kevin Became Host  | Ask This Old House
description: In this video, Ask This Old House host Kevin O'Connor explains how he landed one of the most important jobs on the staffâ€”without even trying.|SUBSCRIBE to This Old House: http://bit.ly/SubscribeThisOldHouse.|Kevin O'Connor explains how he became the host of ASK and This Old House. With a bright future in finance, Kevin and his wife sent in a letter to This Old House about their home at the same time Ask This Old House was starting. A few weeks after the crew performed a house call at Kevin's home, he received the job offer from the production crew, and the rest is history.|Host Kevin O'Connor never dreamed of hosting Ask This Old House, but a string of good luck seemed to drop the job into his lap.|Kevin was always a fan of This Old House and enjoyed working with his hands. When he and his wife bought their first home, they purposely looked for a fixer-upper. After handling some of the projects themselves, the O'Connors sent a letter to the This Old House team.|Unknown to him, a new show was already in the works: Ask This Old House. After receiving his letter, the crew arrived at Kevin's house for a house call. The crew helped Kevin handle some projects around his home, and his personality sparked an interest. About a month later, Kevin received a phone call from the production team asking if he would be interested in hosting the show, and he knew he couldn't turn it down.|While he was excited to take the job, Kevin didn't think it would last long. As he explained his leaving to his then-boss in the finance industry, Kevin asked him to keep a spot open, as he thought he'd be back in the finance world in around 12 months. That was almost 20 years ago.|Kevin got his start by working with the crew of experts and tradespeople. Plumbing and heating expert Richard Trethewey had Kevin dig ditches. General contractor Tom Silva put Kevin to work cutting wood. He built his skillset with on-the-job training, but his excitement for new projects and to learn never needed bolstering.|Kevin's favorite part of his job is when he gets to work side-by-side with the crew. He finds satisfaction in working with his hands and appreciates the opportunity to shift from the host to the crew. He tries to hand his love and satisfaction down to his kids with projects around their home, hoping that it might stick with them. His other hope? That his kids don't work in television.|Looking for more step by step guidance on how to complete projects around the house? Join This Old House Insider to stream over 1,000 episodes commercial-free: https://bit.ly/2GPiYbH|Plus, download our FREE app for full-episode streaming to your connected TV, phone or tablet:  https://www.thisoldhouse.com/pages/streaming-app|About Ask This Old House TV: |From the makers of This Old House, Americaâ€™s first and most trusted home improvement show, Ask This Old House answers the steady stream of home improvement questions asked by viewers across the United States. Covering topics from landscaping to electrical to HVAC and plumbing to painting and more. Ask This Old House features the experts from This Old House, including general contractor Tom Silva, plumbing and heating expert Richard Trethewey, landscape contractor Jenn Nawada, master carpenter Norm Abram, and host Kevin Oâ€™Connor. ASK This Old House helps you protect and preserve your greatest investmentâ€”your home.|Follow This Old House:|Facebook: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHouseFB|Twitter: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHouseTwitter|Pinterest: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHousePinterest|Instagram: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHouseIG|How Kevin Became Host  | Ask This Old House|https://www.youtube.com/user/thisoldhouse/

title: Ina Garten's Roast Duck Breast with Cherries and Port | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network
description: Ina reveals the secret for making this tough meat incredibly tender with her year-round take on an elegant duck dinner!|Subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream more of #BarefootContessa: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd|Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/3yuAvOW|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Ina throws open the doors of her Hamptons home for delicious food, dazzling entertaining ideas and good fun on Barefoot Contessa.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Roast Duck Breast With Dried Cherries and Port|RECIPE COURTESY OF INA GARTEN|Level: Easy|Total: 7 hr 10 min (includes marinating time)|Active: 35 min|Yield: 4 servings|Ingredients|2 (1-pound) or 4 (8-ounce) Moulard duck breasts|Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper |1 tablespoon canola oil |2 tablespoons unsalted butter |1/2 cup minced shallots (2 shallots) |1 1/2 tablespoons good sherry wine vinegar |3/4 cup ruby Port wine |1/2 cup good chicken stock, preferably homemade |1/2 cup dried cherries |1/4 cup creme fraiche |1 teaspoon grated orange zest |1/4 cup freshly squeezed orange juice |Directions|Wrap each duck breast in plastic wrap and pound them with a meat mallet until each breast is about 1 inch thick. Place the duck on a plate, sprinkle both sides with a total of 4 teaspoons salt, cover with plastic wrap, and refrigerate for at least 6 hours or overnight.|When ready to cook the duck, preheat the oven to 375 degrees F.|Score the skin of the duck breasts with a sharp knife, making a crosshatch pattern but not cutting down to the meat.|In a large (12-inch) heavy-bottomed, ovenproof skillet, heat the oil over medium heat. Place the duck breasts in the pan, skin side down. Cook uncovered over medium heat for 12 to 15 minutes, discarding the fat from the pan occasionally, until the skin is very browned. Turn the duck with tongs, place the skillet in the oven, and roast for 12 to 18 minutes, until the internal temperature of the duck is 120 degrees F for rare. Remove from the oven, cover the pan tightly with aluminum foil, and allow the duck to rest for 10 minutes.|Meanwhile, make the sauce. Melt the butter over medium-high heat in a medium saucepan. Add the shallots and saute for 2 minutes, until tender. Add the vinegar and cook for one minute. Add the Port, chicken stock, cherries, 1 teaspoon salt, and 1/2 teaspoon pepper, bring to a boil, lower the heat, and simmer for 15 minutes. Stir in the crÃ¨me fraÃ®che, orange zest, and orange juice and keep warm over low heat.|Transfer the duck to a cutting board and slice diagonally, fanning the slices out on 4 dinner plates. Spoon the sauce generously on top, sprinkle with salt, and serve hot with extra sauce on the side.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|â–¶ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|â–¶ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#InaGarten #BarefootContessa #FoodNetwork #RoastDuckBreast|Ina Garten's Roast Duck Breast with Cherries and Port | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlbZ14SoLqQ

title: Charlo vs Montiel FULL FIGHT: June 19, 2021 | PBC on Showtime
description: (June 19, 2021) Jermall Charlo retained his WBC World Middleweight title and improves to 32-0 (22 KOs) following a dominant unanimous decision victory over rugged Juan Macias Montiel.|Undefeated WBC Middleweight World Champion Jermall Charlo successfully defended his title with a unanimous decision shutout victory over courageous challenger Juan Montiel in an action-packed night of boxing Saturday night live on SHOWTIME from Toyota Center in Houston, Texas in a Premier Boxing Champions event.|Charlo and Montiel both played an equal part in the electrifying main event that capped off a special Juneteenth Day boxing celebration. Charlo threw a career-high 769 punches, yet the gritty, relentless Montiel refused to go down. Instead, Montiel continued to walk forward despite taking incredible punishment, earning Charloâ€™s respect in the process for his guts and character.|Charlo landed more than twice the amount of punches as Montiel (258-127), including a career-high 201 power punches. Montiel miraculously survived a grueling sixth round, despite being on the receiving end of 36 punches landed, a majority of them thrown with malice behind them.  |In the eighth round, Charlo suffered the first cut of his career as Montiel continued to return punches and opened up a gash over Charloâ€™s right eye. Still, Montiel was far out-classed in terms of boxing ability and athleticism. Despite being unable to close the show in front of the raucous hometown crowd, Charlo displayed his well-rounded game, using a variety of punches to deliver shot after shot on Montiel.|#JermallCharlo #CharloMontiel #FullFight|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: Guy Fieri's Smoked Prime Rib with Brown Butter Garlic Sauce | Guy's Big Bite | Food Network
description: Guy rubs the prime rib with a spice mix before smoking it, and prepares a flavorful brown butter sauce with garlic, parsley, rosemary, thyme and shallots!|Subscribe to #discoveryplusâ€‹ to stream more of #GuysBigBiteâ€‹: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgdâ€‹|Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/3NA81aJ|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|We know one thing is certain â€” Guy Fieri's food is as fun, fearless and fundamental as his larger-than-life personality. We hope you're hungry, because this Guy's imagination knows no limits. Open wide for Guy's Big Bite!|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Smoked Prime Rib with Brown Butter Garlic Sauce|RECIPE COURTESY OF GUY FIERI|Level: Intermediate|Total: 3 hr 40 min (includes smoking time)|Active: 40 min|Yield: 4 to 6 servings|Ingredients|Smoked Prime Rib:|2 tablespoons granulated garlic|2 tablespoons freshly ground black pepper |2 tablespoons kosher salt |1 1/2 tablespoons mustard powder |1 tablespoon paprika |1/2 teaspoon cayenne|One 6- to 7-pound bone-in prime rib |3 sprigs fresh oregano |3 sprigs fresh rosemary |3 sprigs fresh thyme |3 tablespoons canola oil |Brown Butter Garlic Sauce:|1/4 cup minced garlic|1/4 cup chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley|1 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper |1 teaspoon fresh rosemary leaves |1 teaspoon fresh thyme leaves |1/2 teaspoon kosher salt |2 shallots, minced |1 stick unsalted butter |1 cup low-sodium beef broth |1/4 cup Worcestershire sauce |1 tablespoon demi-glace|Directions|Special equipment: a charcoal kettle-style grill; charcoal; 8 cups large smoking wood chips (applewood and hickory mix), soaked in water; butcher's twine|For the prime rib: Heat the charcoal until hot, then carefully arrange on one side of a kettle-style grill, and place the soaked wood chips over the hot coals. Place an aluminum pan filled with some water opposite to the coals to catch any drippings. Place a wire rack on the grill. Cover the grill to allow the smoke to accumulate and preheat to about 225 degrees F.|In a small bowl, add the granulated garlic, black pepper, salt, mustard powder, paprika and cayenne, and mix well. Rub the spice mixture all over the prime rib, then set aside. Combine the oregano, rosemary and thyme and tie together with butcher's twine. In a large cast-iron pan set over medium-high heat, add the oil. Rub the oil all over the pan using the herb bundle, then set aside. Place the prime rib fat-side down in the pan and sear until browned, 7 to 8 minutes. Flip over and sear the other side until browned, 4 to 5 minutes. Turn on its end and sear for 2 minutes.|Place the prime rib on the grill over the aluminum pan, with the thick end facing the coals. Place the lid on the grill. Smoke the prime rib until the internal temperature reaches 130 degrees F for medium-rare, 2 hours 30 minutes to 3 hours.|Remove the prime rib to a baking sheet and set aside to rest.|For the sauce: In a medium saute pan set over medium-high heat, add the garlic, parsley, black pepper, rosemary, thyme, salt, shallots and butter. Cook, stirring continuously, until the butter foams and the garlic turns a light golden color, 5 to 6 minutes. Add the broth, Worcestershire and demi-glace. Stir to combine, and cook until the sauce reduces by one-third, remove from the heat and set aside.|If the chine bone has been removed, slice the prime rib into generous 1-bone portions. Otherwise, slice off the bone and cut into generous portions, and then place on a platter. Spoon the sauce over the top, and serve.|Cookâ€™s Note|This recipe can be made in an oven if you do not have a charcoal kettle-style grill. I coimputati nel processo, Francesco Belleggia e Mario Pincarelli sono stati condannati rispettivamente a 23 e 21 anni.
