title: Ukraine braces for more attacks in Donetsk as it outlines a $750 billion plan to rebuild | DW News
description: Ukrainian officials now anticipate more attacks against the city of Slovyansk, as Russian forces move further west. Russia now occupies all of Luhansk, and about half of Donetsk - the two regions which make up the Donbas. But a defense advisor told DW Moscow is yet to establish its control of the area. |Kyiv is also making post-war reconstruction plans. Ukrainian Prime Minister Denys Shmyhal told the Ukraine Recovery Conference in Lugano that the country needs $750 billion (â‚¬718 billion) for a three-stage recovery plan. title: UHOH! FOUND A WEAKNESS - First Aston Martin DBS Nurburgring Laps
description: I couldn't be in Germany with my Aston Martin DBS and not take it for a first lap at the NÃ¼rburgring Nordschleife! After a blast up the derestricted Autobahn to let the V12 purr, let's see how it handles the famous Green Hell as it follows the rite of passage for all Shmeemobiles.|Having made a spontaneous trip to the continent and a long journey out, it's almost immediately time to turn back around for the return journey, this time taking in some stretches of the famously open speed-limited German motorways. With busy roads all over due to the holiday season, there are only a few moments to let the V12 come to life until arrival in the Eifel Mountains.|Nearly all members of my garage have at some point been for a lap at the NÃ¼rburgring, and of course the Aston Martin DBS has to be no exception. While it is very much a grand touring in character, and perhaps rather soft for the bumpy undulations of this particular loop, it's still very much a fun time putting down the power and enjoying a Touristenfahrten session.|Afterwards it's straight back on the road for the onward journey back to London; a total day drive of over 1,000km (600+ miles) and about 15 hours on the road.|Awesome thumbnail pic from GT Carshots, be sure to check out pics of your laps and GP sessions at RaceTracker.de as well!|https://www.racetracker.de|https://www.instagram.com/gt.carshots/|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:03 Heading to the NÃ¼rburgring|02:31 Autobahn Leg|07:14 Arriving in NÃ¼rburg|09:06 Nordschleife Lap|19:12 Onwards to the UK|20:33 Arrival at the Eurotunnel|22:55 Welcome to the UK|23:10 We've Arrived|24:24 Wrap Up|#AstonMartin #Nurburgring #RoadTrip|||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: New Dragon Ball Super: Super Hero Details Revealed - IGN The Fix: Entertainment
description: A new Dragon Ball Super: Super Hero trailer has emerged, revealing what's in store for Piccolo, Gohan, and the rest of the Z-Fighters in the upcoming Dragon Ball Super movie. In the new #DragonBallSuper Super Hero promo, we finally see one of the major antagonists of the film, Cell Max. Obviously not the Perfect Cell we've been hoping to see make a return to the Dragon Ball franchise, but this is a good sign that the classic DBZ character is still likely to make a comeback at some point. We break down the new DBS anime trailer. In other news, the Horizon television series is apparently named Horizon 2074, which likely means it's set during the fall of civilization. And finally, One Piece Day is coming our way!|#IGN

We laten je regionaal nieuws zien uit de regio's Zwolle, Deventer, Almelo, Enschede, Vechtdal, Kop van Overijssel en de Reggestreek. Daarnaast brengen we je spraakmakende documentaires over bijvoorbeeld de vuurwerkramp in Enschede, Lotte van der Zee, Krav Maga en we gaan langs bij bekende mensen uit onze regio en brengen je het laatste nieuws van vandaag.|âœ‰ï¸ Heb je een tip? title: Eye on AMCA fighter project & IAFâ€™s Rafale, French engine makerâ€™s MRO facility in India soon
description: Giving a further boost to the Narendra Modi government's ambitious 'Aatmanirbhar Bharat' campaign, French engine-maker Safran will set up a Maintenance Repair and Overhaul facility for leading-edge aviation propulsion (LEAP) commercial aircraft engines. The MRO facility will be set up by the company as part of its offset commitments. As per reports, Safran will invest $150 million in setting up the facility. Sources told HT that the MRO facility, said to be based either in Hyderabad or Bengaluru, will apparently be announced tomorrow when Safran CEO Olivier Andres meets Indian Civil Aviation Minister Jyotiraditya Scindia. It also aims to further its proposal to co-develop with DRDO's Gas Turbine Research Establishment a 110kn thrust engine for the fifth-generation advanced medium combat aircraft twin-engine (AMCA) fighter project. Watch this video for more details.|#india #france #defence #amcafighterjet #rafalefighter #aircraftengine #rafale #safran #aircraftmaintenance #narendramodi #jyotiradityascindia #emmanuelmacron

title: OBI-WAN KENOBI Plot Holes EXPLAINED and Questions Answered
description: Obi-Wan Kenobi wrapped up its story, linking two trilogies of the Star Wars saga. But the final confrontation with Darth Vader and his fond farewell with Princess Leia left a lot of fans scratching their heads. Weâ€™ve collected your unanswered questions and plot holes, and now we;re here to answer them.|If you're new, Subscribe! â†’ http://bit.ly/subscribe-screencrush|Go here â†’ http://screencrush.com/|Like us â†’ https://www.facebook.com/ScreenCrush|Follow us â†’ https://twitter.com/screencrushnews|Get our newsletter â†’ http://screencrush.com/newsletter/|Written and Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)|Edited by Srinidhi Rao, Ethan Lavinsky, and Randolf Nombrado|#ObiWanKenobi #PlotHoles #StarWars |Lots of people asked why Darth Vader left Reva alive instead of killing her. Harry Syed says: â€œVader killing random civilians like whatevs and then just letting obi-wan escape and Reva live after she tried to kill him.â€|Obviously, the number one reason why he left Reva alive was so she could go scour the shire and give Ben some hope for the future [clip]. And to probably set up her own spinoff. |But, Vader sparing her makes sense within the show. For Reva's entire life, Vader has been using her. The moment she joined the inquisitors, he recognized her. [did you think I wouldn;t know you youngling]. So heâ€™s always known that she wanted revenge, but he kept her around anywaysâ€“because she was never a threat to him. He saw her as someone he could use and throw away. [you are of no further use]|As for Reva, we don;t really see where Vader stabbed her. It's a wide shot. It could have been a wound that missed vital organs, and the blade cauterized the wound so she wouldn;t bleed out. But also, the show is better if she lives and we get a final scene with her. |J Pollocks Number 5 on twitter asks: If Vader is so all powerful and can detect people at other times (ANH) Reva etc. - how can he not even know his kids are about? In Kenobi and ANH Leia is in his presence When DOES he find out he has them?|Great question, and I have actual answers. First of all, Vder does not know his kids are alive. He thought they died with Padme [no, she was alive]. So he would never look at Leia and think, â€œOh sheâ€™s the spitting image of Padme, I bet thatâ€™s my daughter.â€ In fact, a person who looks like Padme would make Vader want to AVOID thinking about the babies, because the memory is too painful.â€|In a new hope. Vader deos sense the Force around Lukeâ€™s X-Wing, but only after Ben's ghost tells Luke to stretch out with his feelings [clip, force is strong]. So originally the Force is portrayed as being dormant until someone learns to awaken it. Kylo Ren also didnâ€™t get much of a force sensitivity vibe off Rey, at first.|Whereas he knows Kenobi's mind very well, and would have sensed him immediately. As for when Vader found out, the 2015 Darth Vader comic takes place right after a New Hope. Vader goes on a mission to discover who destroyed the Death Star, and Boba Fett tracks down a name: Skywalker. Thatâ€™s when Vader realizes the emperor lied to him about Padme [in your angerâ€¦]|Vader is pissed when he realizes this, and then decides to overthrow the Emperor, which is why he makes this offer to Luke [join meâ€¦]|Burt Macklin 70 asks, â€œAlso wouldn't the empire come down on alderaan after seeing Leia associating with the path?â€|Now that is interesting. Reva researched Bail and Obi Wanâ€™s relationship, and exploited it by kidnapping Leia. So essentially, she revealed that Bail organa knew how to contact at least one Jedi Master. I think they didnâ€™t go after Bail Organa for 2 reasons. One, the Imperial senate is still a governing body that the emperor needs to control the systems. Itâ€™s not gone for another 7 years. So Vail organa would have a lot of political influence, and would be useful to the Empire.|Plus, there is no actual proof linking Baila and the Jedi. When you get into the canon novels, you see that evidence and protocol were very important within the empire.|But the main reason they didn;t come down on Alderaan is because the emperor said not to [feelings are clear]. Vaderâ€™s pursuit of Ben Kenobi was about getting revenge for Anakin. And the emperor doesn;t want Vader to do anything on Anakinâ€™s behalf, because Anakin is dead. Palpatine believes that the few Jedi remaining could not possibly threaten his big, bad Death Star.|Dynasty Dopamine asks, â€œI can handle all these. I just want to know why Tala, an experienced soldier, stands in the middle of the hallway without cover while engaging in a gunfight.â€ |Just watch the scene again. There is one point where she is standing next to some cover. But she stands her ground because her objective is to take down as many stormtroopers as she can, not to protect herself. Then theyâ€™re slowly forced back the corridor, away from any cover. She doesnâ€™t go for cover because sheâ€™s there to be a shield between the refugees and the empire.

title: Taliban minister asked when Afghan girls can return to school - BBC News
description: The Taliban's health minister has said there are "some concerns" about the separate system of teenage girls' education in Afghanistan.|It is 290 days since the Taliban banned girls from attending secondary schools.|Taliban Public Health Minister Dr Qalandar Ebad said: "The teaching of Islam states that men and women are equal, that is clearâ€¦ but we have some concerns about the syllabus, we have some concerns about the hijab and some concerns about the separate system.â€|It comes as human rights groups have criticised an all-male gathering of more than 4,500 of Taliban leaders, clerics and leaders for not addressing concerns about the rights of women and girls.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Afghanistan #BBCNews

title: Kejanggalan yang Disorot Tempo dalam Pengelolaan ACT
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV -  Presiden ACT, Ibnu Khajar memberi tanggapan soal dugaan penyelewangan yang diungkap Tempo.||||Ibnu Khajar menyatakan kondisi keuangan ACT saat ini dalam keadaan baik.||||Terkait dengan besaran gaji pimpinan ACT yang sempat ditulis Tempo dengan nilai fantastis, Presiden ACT justru mengklaim telah terjadi pengurangan gaji.||||Jika dugaan tersebut benar, lalu berapa besar nilai pemborosan dan penyewengan yang dilakukan?||||Lalu bagaimana pertanggung jawabannya pada donatur dan publik?||||Kami membahasnya bersama dua  narasumber  yaitu Direktur Pemberitaan Tempo Budi Setyarso bersama Wakil Ketua Komisi VIII DPR Ace Hasan Syadzily. ||||----||||Sahabat Kompas TV juga bisa memperoleh informasi terkini melalui website: https://www.kompas.tv ||||Media sosial Kompas TV:||||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KompasTV ||||Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kompastv ||||Twitter: https://twitter.com/KompasTV |||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305815/kejanggalan-yang-disorot-tempo-dalam-pengelolaan-act

title: How Stranger Things' Joseph Quinn Learned To Play Metallica's 'Master Of Puppets' | News
description: The finale of 'Stranger Things' season 4 featured a performance of Metallica's classic 'Master Of Puppets'. Eddie Munson actor Joseph Quinn has revealed in a new interview how he learned to play the track, which featured additional guitar work from Rob Trujillo's son Tye. The song has shot up the global Spotify chart as a result of being featured in the finale - could it see the same level of success as Kate Bush's 'Running Up That Hill'? Plus, Jamie Campbell Bower talks the importance of music to the Netflix show and we look back into the archive as BABYMETAL, Trivium and Biffy Clyro tell us what Metallica mean to them.|Host: James Wilson-Taylor|#Metallica #StrangerThings #MasterOfPuppets|Subscribe to Rock Sound's YouTube channel: http://bit.ly/XYvFPb||||Get the best interviews, music videos and more from the wide world of alternative music.||See what else we do: http://www.rocksound.tv||||Rock Sound Magazine is available worldwide: ||Download the digital edition: http://smarturl.it/rsapp ||Order a copy direct to your door: http://shop.rocksound.tv

title: After Lysychansk, Russia Eyes Sloviansk l Why This Battle Can Help Putin Achieve Ukraine War Goal
description: After Russia captured the eastern Ukrainian city of Lysychansk, its troops are turning their attention to the city of Sloviansk. Residents of Sloviansk, a city of just over 100,000 people before the invasion, are now being urged to evacuate. As per reports, Russian troops were attempting to push Ukrainian forces back to a new defensive line between Siversk, Soledar and Bakhmut. On July 3, Ukrainian authorities said six people were killed in the Russian shelling of Sloviansk and another 19 people were wounded.|#RussiaUkraineWar #Sloviansk #BattleForDonbas|0:00 - INTRODUCTION|1:30 - WILL HISTORY REPEAT ITSELF IN SLOVIANSK?|2:12 -IMPORTANCE OF SLOVIANSK |CRUX is your daily video news guide to the big events that are shaping our world. title: Big GC Shakeup! | Giro Donne 2022 Stage 4 Highlights

This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. title: DUNCAN FERGUSON'S FAREWELL | Everton Giant leaves to pursue managerial ambition
description: Everton can confirm that Duncan Ferguson has left his role as First-Team Assistant Manager to pursue his managerial ambition.|The Club legend, inducted as an Everton Giant in 2011 after two memorable stints as a player at Goodison Park -  in which he captained the side under three different managers - returned to the Blues to coach in the Academy that same year and in 2014, after working as Under-18s Assistant Manager and gaining his UEFA Pro coaching licence, was promoted to a position with the First Team.|The Scot underlined his iconic status with two spells as caretaker manager. title: Then and Now: Jimmy Kimmel's First and Last Appearances on 'The Ellen Show'
description: Jimmy Kimmel visited Ellen in 2004 to share what was going on with his health, Halloween, and the third season of his late-night talk show. In 2021 he returned to share the latest with his kids and be the first guest of the last season for this 20th appearance.

title: 'I Sent Naked Selfies Of Myself Aged 13 - It Almost Destroyed Me & My Family' | This Morning
description: A recent survey found that 60% of teenage girls under the age of 18 have been asked by a boy to send a nude photo of themselves - with a third of the girls surveyed saying they were first asked when they were under the age of 13. Mother Gay Longworth discovered her 13-year-old daughter Roxy had been coerced into sending explicit images to a boy four years her senior when she received a phonecall from her school. The photos were spreading around Roxyâ€™s peers like wildfire, leading to Roxy dropping out of school with severe mental health issues. title: Komisi VIII DPR RI: Kasus Gagal Haji Furoda Berindikasi Penipuan

title: Petir Bukan Sembarang Petir, Ini Dia Kompilasi Stand Up Indra Jegel
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Menuju satu dekade, Stand Up Comedy Indonesia banyak melahirkan komika-komika hebat yang kini dikenal masyarakat. Selama 9 season, Stand Up Comedy Indonesia juga menghasilkan 9 juara.||||Kali ini, kami akan flashback ke-9 komika yang menjadi juara 1 SUCI dengan menghadirkan kompilasi stand up comedy terbaik dari masing-masing juara. ||||Di tahun 2016, Stand Up Comedy Indonesia kembali memiliki sang juara stand up comedy yaitu Indra Jegel. Dengan jargonnya yaitu 'Petir Bukan Sembarang Petir', pria kelahiran Medan tahun 1989 ini berhasil meraih juara 1 SUCI 6.||||Setelah menang dari SUCI 6, Indra Jegel melanjutkan karirnya sebagai stand up komedian dan juga mulai bermain film.||||Berikut merupakan kompilasi stand up comedy Indra Jegel saat show SUCI 6.||||------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------||||Follow dan subscribe:||||Instagram: @sucikompastv||||Twitter: @StandUpKompasTV||||TikTok: @suci_kompastv||||Facebook: @standupkompastv||||YouTube: Stand Up Kompas TV||||Website: suci.kompas.tv||||#IndraJegel #SUCI6||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305783/petir-bukan-sembarang-petir-ini-dia-kompilasi-stand-up-indra-jegel

Chief Minister Eknath Shinde's Speech In Assembly After Trust Vote Win
description: Eknath Shinde broke down today in an emotional speech in the Maharashtra assembly, his first as Chief Minister after an easy trust vote win. While describing what he alleged were threats to his family over his revolt, Eknath Shinde referred to two of his children who had died and choked up. "They attacked my family...My father is alive, my mother died. I could not give much time to my parents. They would be asleep when I came and would go to work when I slept. I could not give much time to my son Shrikant. My two children died - at the time, Anand Dighe consoled me. I used to think, what is there to live for? title: Taliban commander flies bride in military chopper in Afghanistan? Video goes viral
description: A Taliban commander allegedly used military helicopter to take newly-wed bride home in Afghanistan. Afghan media reports claim that the commander allegedly flew his newlywed bride from Logar to Khost province, in eastern Afghanistan, using the military helicopter. In a video that went viral on social media, the commander is seen as landing near a house. Taliban have dismissed the video and claims as false and enemy propaganda. Watch the video for more.|#taliban #afghanistan #chopper #taliban #logar #haqqaninetwork #usarmy #viralvideo #kabul #khost

title: Rivera vs Fernandez FULL FIGHT: July 3, 2021 | PBC on Showtime
description: (July 3, 2021)   Unbeaten rising star Michel Rivera stuns lightweight contender Jon FernÃ¡ndez with an eighth-round KO victory during their 135-pound WBA title eliminator.|Rising lightweight contender Michel Rivera (21-0, 14 KOs) scored a highlight-reel knockout over Jon Fernandez (21-2, 18 KOs) in the eighth round of their WBA Lightweight Title Eliminator. |The 23-year-old was able to weather the storm brought by the Spaniard Fernandez and made it through the round despite the knockdown.
